{"tid":2436982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇周星馳有去=被壓力迫， 無去=無人性？","createTime":"2021-03-07T14:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T06:50:10.000Z","uid":34571,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0c1c2c2e7e899e22f89b7a4250d8f7f82bf12a23","tid":2436982,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T14:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WhC6cOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhC6cOV.jpg&h=6c18b10d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前牌就有post話佢有錢佬死先會去見，係無人性，依家去公祭又有人好肯定好肯定咁話係有壓力先去，一方面話人屈對白比佢，自己一方面又屈原因比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23e717065233bdd1c5c1b83f0c89175bbfb65a6a","tid":2436982,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565fd791a5aab268e31d878c91d4b9ea078d66dc","tid":2436982,"uid":22059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"兒登仔講乜都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45bf6a28ce2090afcf36fdb87ea051e5e4297d10","tid":2436982,"uid":78243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:18:23.000Z","msg":"周星馳做咩唔自殺殉情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"311ce3a6cb8ee172169a3e041d45916b04f3393c","tid":2436982,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:34:52.000Z","msg":"因為條友乞人憎<br />\n做咩都唔順眼"},{"pid":"a66ff90c63cbc7def66fcb82f2fa6a11f73cd4a8","tid":2436982,"uid":58031,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"證明一個人平時嘅言行舉指累積落嚟嘅形象有幾重要<br />\n你平時做野好好睇睇嘅，做咩都順眼；相反就做咩都唔順眼"},{"pid":"2bd0f004f253acdfa92e3e36f57f83e1220821f8","tid":2436982,"uid":209662,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"每個月都要post幾次個故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有父子兩個人趕著一頭驢去趕集。一開始他們是趕著驢走，走著走著，他們碰到了一些人，這些人看到父子倆趕著驢在地上走，於是就紛紛地嘲笑說，這父子倆真是太傻了，放著驢不騎，卻跟著驢子在地上跑。聽了這樣的嘲諷，那個父親就騎上驢繼續向前趕路。<br />\n<br />\n結果走著走著，他們又碰上了另一些人，這些人看到父親騎在驢上，又很不滿意了，他們紛紛指責說，看看這個父親是多麼不知道疼愛兒子啊，他的兒子那麼小，身體那麼單薄，可他卻堂而皇之地騎在驢上，讓兒子在地上跟著跑。聽了這些人的指責，這個父親就跳下了驢，讓兒子騎到驢上繼續向前趕路。<br />\n<br />\n結果走著走著，他們又碰到了一些人，這些人看到兒子騎在驢上又不高興了，他們說，看看這個兒子多麼不知道孝順父親啊，他的父親年紀那麼大了，他卻心安理得地騎在驢上，讓父親在地上跑。聽了這樣的指責，兒子就請他的父親又騎到了驢上，兩個人同時騎著驢向前趕路。<br />\n<br />\n結果走著走著，他們又碰到了一些人，這些人發現父子倆居然同時都騎在驢上，就紛紛指責說，你們看這父子倆多麼沒有同情心，那個驢子那麼瘦小，可是他們居然同時騎在驢上，都要把它累死了。聽到這樣的指責之後，這父子倆感到無所適從，因為怎麼做都不對，怎麼做都會有人指責，想來想去他們也想不出好辦法。最後大家知道他們是怎麼樣來到集市上的嗎？他們抬著驢來到了集市上。<br />\n<br />\n故事固然有一些誇張，但是這個故事告訴我們，人們在日常生活中擔憂的事情太多了，或者是太在乎外在的評價給自己的暗示，就會產生種種不必要的擔心，從而自我加壓。不必要的擔心不僅僅限制了自己的遠見，也會使自己作出一些愚蠢的不必要的行為。"},{"pid":"86457b73c5b1755d6ed80828ad0c9fccecd709ef","tid":2436982,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"好難聽，但who fucking care 連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec61922404d8f684b7ea9b46b41a3c0b5920161e","tid":2436982,"uid":129658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45bf6a28ce2090afcf36fdb87ea051e5e4297d10","tid":2436982,"uid":78243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:18:23.000Z","msg":"周星馳做咩唔自殺殉情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:59:45.000Z","msg":"咁又會比人話造作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50872372d94771ca8956da676bb0216c0a6bd1e1","tid":2436982,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:00:46.000Z","msg":"WFC"},{"pid":"92f4b71a562ec53a9474ae1b3cd0ee5f52fc438e","tid":2436982,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ec61922404d8f684b7ea9b46b41a3c0b5920161e","tid":2436982,"uid":129658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"45bf6a28ce2090afcf36fdb87ea051e5e4297d10","tid":2436982,"uid":78243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:18:23.000Z","msg":"周星馳做咩唔自殺殉情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:59:45.000Z","msg":"咁又會比人話造作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:03:17.000Z","msg":"死左都話人造作，有無人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e2426cb884f029ee95c796d30db899e4307475","tid":2436982,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:04:06.000Z","msg":"上連登 勿認真"},{"pid":"a66bf664f6ebd115145f2ced8bc00e08261f1a44","tid":2436982,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:12:20.000Z","msg":"最後幾交惡都好<br />\n星仔點會唔去拜三叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2be952a3453436e70a954246cbd44724f38bf7b","tid":2436982,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a66bf664f6ebd115145f2ced8bc00e08261f1a44","tid":2436982,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:12:20.000Z","msg":"最後幾交惡都好<br />\n星仔點會唔去拜三叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:46:46.000Z","msg":"受壓力去咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1d90a5edaebc2527476c6d2a41d3cda342c178","tid":2436982,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"565fd791a5aab268e31d878c91d4b9ea078d66dc","tid":2436982,"uid":22059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"兒登仔講乜都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:50:10.000Z","msg":"兒登仔個撚個都自我到爆<br />\n人地覺得唔係既話<br />\n就一定人地唔識野/係傻仔etc<br />\n永遠都係自己無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知係咪細路特別多"}]}